title: Craig Lieberman (Technical Advisor for The Fast and Furious)
description:
Craig Lieberman was a technical advisor on the first two films of the "Fast and Furious" franchise. He has amazing stories from those productions, all of which he documents on his website and YouTube channel. He was also the original owner of the Supra, R34 GT-R & Maxima from the first two Fast & Furious movies.

 

http://fastandfuriousfacts.com/

 

Watch the show here! https://youtu.be/poRc6APj3Kg
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
